data.title: Om Shanti Om
data.meta_description: Om Shanti Om (2007) starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone, Arjun Rampal and directed by Farah Khan.
data.text: In the 1970s, Om, an aspiring actor, is murdered, but is immediately reincarnated into the present day. He attempts to discover the mystery of his demise and find Shanti, the love of his previous life.
